One of the big mistakes that I
find that people make when they're

13
00:00:52.340 --> 00:00:57.374
asking people to act, is they ask
them to do too many things, right?

14
00:00:57.374 --> 00:01:00.221
And again,
we're gonna come on to this more later.

15
00:01:00.221 --> 00:01:03.815
But we want you to buy our product,
sign up for

16
00:01:03.815 --> 00:01:08.555
our newsletter, get in touch,
follow us on social media.

17
