that emotional blackmail, right?

96
00:06:29.399 --> 00:06:32.090
Saying donate to end
the suffering of children,

97
00:06:32.090 --> 00:06:36.825
especially if it read something like, do I
want to reduce the suffering of children.

98
00:06:36.825 --> 00:06:41.703
It could be emotional blackmail and so you
need to be careful with your audience and

99
00:06:41.703 --> 00:06:43.337
see how they respond to it.

100
00:06:43.337 --> 00:06:48.061
But the principle of taking something
complex and simplifying it down so

101
00:06:48.061 --> 00:06:52.486
it's easily understandable needs
to underpin all of our content.

